{"TopicId":192838,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"(April Fool\u0027s Gag): Dec 1 release date plus KSP 2 goes VR-only like HL:Alyx","CreatedByName":"Chilkoot","CreatedById":175911,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T13:41:34Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Chilkoot","CreatedById":175911,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T13:41:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow - two big announcements today (screenshot below).\u00A0 Here\u0027s a text copy from the website:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EKerbal Space Program 2, the sequel to the acclaimed space flight game from Private\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EDivision, will be lithobraking on Earth \u003Cb\u003EDecember 1\u003Csup\u003Est\u003C/sup\u003E, 2020\u003C/b\u003E.\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E\u00A0\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E[image][image]\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E\u00A0\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EWith the original Kerbal Space Program having become one of the most beloved games\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003Eof all time, and now bigger than ever, Kerbal Space Program 2 has been fully redesigned\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003Efrom the ground up to meet the demands of modern and next-generation space\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003Eexploration, all while maintaining the monumental foundations of the first game.\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003ETo deliver the most immersive and engaging experience possible, we are very excited to\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003Eannounce that Kerbal Space Program 2 will be \u003Cb\u003Eexclusively playable in Virtual Reality\u003C/b\u003E! \u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EKerbonauts will feel the engines roar to life as they lift off from \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E, gaze out the command\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003Epod window while their craft eases to a landing, and reach down to gather rock samples\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003Efrom the surface of M\u00FCn.\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0 \u003C/span\u003EKerbal Space Program 2 is compatible with all major Virtual\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EReality platforms including SteamVR, Oculus Rift, Windows Mixed Reality and PSVR.\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00229Bt9vXR.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002280.18\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 width=\u0022957\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/9Bt9vXR.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-02T01:34:23Z\u0022 title=\u002204/02/2020 01:34  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 2, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Chilkoot\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Selective Genius","CreatedById":197502,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T13:54:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope, from the bottom of my heart that this is an April Fool\u0027s joke... Because if it\u0027s only playable in VR, then it has already lost my interest.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T14:36:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223764513\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585748494\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022175911\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Chilkoot\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n54 minutes ago, Chilkoot said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nM\u00FCn\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T14:48:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/175911-chilkoot/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022175911\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/175911-chilkoot/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Chilkoot\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this some sort of April Fools? Because I navigated to the same page as you (as far as I can see) and I see no such announcement. Besides, if something like this was announced it would have a post in the Announcements section of the forum too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf KSP2 is VR-only now, then it\u0027s lost my interest. I don\u0027t have a VR headset, and can\u0027t afford to sink \u00A3300\u002B into one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dirkidirk","CreatedById":200064,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T14:59:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223764517\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585749254\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197502\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Selective Genius\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Selective Genius said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope, from the bottom of my heart that this is an April Fool\u0027s joke... Because if it\u0027s only playable in VR, then it has already lost my interest.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nme too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T15:36:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wouldn\u0027t believe this on any day.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TaintedLion","CreatedById":137942,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T15:57:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah I highly doubt the devs would willingly decimate their playerbase like this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nansuchao","CreatedById":135151,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T16:14:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHyper LOL!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nightside","CreatedById":150244,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T16:18:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022players will feel the engines roar to life...\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaptic chair compatibility confirmed!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T16:20:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223764513\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585748494\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022175911\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Chilkoot\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Chilkoot said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow - two big announcements today (screenshot below).\u00A0 Here\u0027s a text copy from the website:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E(realistic looking picture)\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery well done. We need some comic relieve in these isolated days!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mieyo","CreatedById":193573,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T16:51:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope this is april fools lmao\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Incarnation of Chaos","CreatedById":197414,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T18:25:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPls be an april fool\u0027s joke; i have no interest in strapping a monitor to my skull and flailing my arms around like a goof. Especially since i have to pay \u0026gt;200 USD for the privilege, and KSP doesn\u0027t gain anything from it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T18:35:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223764721\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585765509\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197414\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Incarnation of Chaos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Incarnation of Chaos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni have no interest in strapping a monitor to my skull and flailing my arms around like a goof.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou don\u0027t know what you\u0027re missing out on, man!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022FCU4YX7HN829Z5O.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022150.23\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 width=\u0022511\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.instructables.com/ORIG/FCU/4YX7/HN829Z5O/FCU4YX7HN829Z5O.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ArtemisAZ","CreatedById":179669,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T21:04:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis actually got me gosh dang it. You\u0027ve bamboozled me for the last time!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Not gonna lie though VR KSP2 would be pretty lit, especially with some haptic feedback stuff like chairs or that weird haptic suit)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T21:08:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis would have been more\u00A0believable\u00A0\u00A0without the VR stuff\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-01T21:08:47Z\u0022 title=\u002204/01/2020 09:08  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 1, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by linuxgurugamer\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chilkoot","CreatedById":175911,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-02T01:36:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223764816\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585775301\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis would have been more\u00A0believable\u00A0\u00A0without the VR stuff\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Pandarin in WoW started as an April Fool\u0027s gag... one never knows!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-02T01:45:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223764917\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585791409\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022175911\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Chilkoot\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Chilkoot said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Pandarin in WoW started as an April Fool\u0027s gag\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI didn\u0027t know that but if you put up a list of things and said one of them was from an April Fool\u0027s gag, I\u0027d have guessed it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich of these was an April Fool\u0027s gag that ended up being real?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nHorse Armor\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLoot Boxes\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe Pandarin from WoW\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOrange Jool\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chilkoot","CreatedById":175911,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-02T01:48:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223764919\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585791922\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI didn\u0027t know that but if you put up a list of things and said one of them was from an April Fool\u0027s gag, I\u0027d have guessed it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich of these was an April Fool\u0027s gag that ended up being real?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nHorse Armor\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLoot Boxes\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe Pandarin from WoW\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOrange Jool\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen I first heard about horse armor, I literally thought it was some kind of prank.\u00A0 I didn\u0027t believe it until my brother-in-law handed me a CD with the content on it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rmaine","CreatedById":143945,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-02T02:52:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223764816\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585775301\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis would have been more\u00A0believable\u00A0\u00A0without the VR stuff\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah. To have VR as an option might have been sort of half plausible. Not very, but at least sort of. But VR exclusively? That\u0027s so implausible that my first thought was that someone didn\u0027t know what the word \u0022exclusively\u0022 meant. \u003Cspan\u003E:-)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chilkoot","CreatedById":175911,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-02T04:33:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223764946\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221585795922\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022143945\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022rmaine\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, rmaine said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo have VR as an option might have been sort of half plausible. Not very, but at least sort of.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s absolutely plausible, but it would be difficult to do well due to the multiple game modes and screens.\u00A0 The best VR titles today typically have only one or two \u0022views\u0022, and any interactive screens like, for example, the tech tree selection in KSP1, would be overlays in a real-world environment - like a screen you walk up to or a book you open.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor a solid VR interface, you generally have to plan for it from day one, as retrofitting VR controls without forethought, esp. for a multi-view game like the current KSP would be messy and may never feel natural.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kspnerd122","CreatedById":199169,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-03T15:09:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nif it is only for VR it will be ##########\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HansonKerman","CreatedById":185809,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-11T17:35:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003Elol nice photoshopping.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}